repair.repairedDockerfile:
# Using Python Slim-Buster
FROM skyzuxzy/skyzu-userbot:buster
# Userbot Telegram 
# By Skyzuu-Userbot 

RUN apt-get update && apt-get upgrade -y
RUN apt-get install --no-install-recommends ffmpeg -y
RUN curl -f -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_16.x | bash - && \
    apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y nodejs && \
    npm i -g npm

RUN git clone -b Skyzuu-Userbot https://github.com/Skyzu/skyzu-userbot /root/userbot
RUN mkdir /root/userbot/.bin
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir --upgrade pip setuptools
WORKDIR /root/userbot

#Install python requirements
RUN pip3 install --no-cache-dir -r https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Skyzu/skyzu-userbot/Skyzuu-Userbot/requirements.txt

EXPOSE 80 443

# Finalization
CMD ["python3", "-m", "userbot"]
